    tuanEn: 'How great is the Creative Force! All things begin here. Clouds move and rain falls, giving form to all creatures. Understanding the cycle of beginning and end, the six stages unfold in perfect timing. Through transformation, everything finds its true nature and grand harmony.',
    philosophy: '乾卦象征天道刚健，核心智慧是"自强不息"——像天体运行一样永不停歇地向上进取。六爻皆阳，代表最纯粹的创造力和生命力。',
    philosophyEn: 'This is the most powerful hexagram - pure creative energy. Just as the sun rises every morning without fail, you are called to pursue your goals with unwavering dedication. Six unbroken lines mean unlimited potential, but also the responsibility to use power wisely.',
    vernacular: '乾卦：大吉大利，吉祥的占卜。',
    vernacularEn: 'Excellent fortune! You possess tremendous creative power right now. The universe gives you a green light to pursue your dreams. But remember: the higher you climb, the more carefully you must step. Stay humble even as you rise.',
    duanyi: '乾卦为纯阳之卦，万物之始。象征天，刚健不息。乾为天、为君、为父、为金、为玉、为冰、为大赤、为良马。所占之事，大亨通，但须守持正固。',
    duanyiEn: 'The hexagram of pure yang energy, origin of all things. It represents Heaven - strong and ceaseless. Qian symbolizes the sky, rulers, fathers, gold, jade, and fine horses. Whatever you seek will prosper greatly, but you must stay true to your principles.',
    shaoYong: '刚健中正，自强不息。\n得此卦者，天行刚健，自强不息，名利双收，但须谨防盛极必衰，宜知进退。',
    shaoYongEn: 'Strong, balanced, and ceaselessly improving.\nIf you receive this hexagram, you are aligned with Heaven\'s strength. Fame and fortune are within reach. But beware: what rises must eventually fall. Know when to advance and when to retreat.',
    fuPeiRong: {
      shiyun: '临事刚健，发展势头强劲，但盛极必衰，宜居安思危。',
      shiyunEn: 'Your momentum is powerful right now. But peaks lead to valleys. Enjoy success while preparing for change.',
      caiyun: '大利可图，但须审时度势，见好就收。',
      caiyunEn: 'Great profits are possible. But know when to take your gains - don\'t let greed turn victory into defeat.',
      jiazhai: '家道兴隆，但须谦逊持家，防止骄奢。',
      jiazhaiEn: 'Family fortunes are rising. Keep your household humble and avoid showing off prosperity.',
      shenti: '注意头部疾病，宜多休息养神。',
      shentiEn: 'Watch for headaches or stress. Rest your mind regularly - even the sun sets each day.'
    },
    traditional: {
      daxiang: '天行健，君子效法天道刚健运行，自强不息，奋发向上。',
      daxiangEn: 'Heaven moves with unfailing strength. Follow this example: never stop improving, never stop striving.',
      yunshi: '飞龙在天，名利双收，但须知进退存亡，物极必反之理。',
      yunshiEn: 'Like a dragon soaring through clouds - fame and fortune are yours. But remember: everything that peaks must eventually descend.',
      shiye: '大吉大利，万事如意，有很强的开创力。但切勿骄傲自满，过于激进，要知进知退。',
      shiyeEn: 'Excellent for career moves! Your creative power is at its peak. But don\'t become arrogant. The wise leader knows when to advance and when to pause.',
      jingshang: '十分顺利，可获大利，但须居安思危，随时注意市场动态。',
      jingshangEn: 'Business prospects are excellent. Big profits possible. But stay alert to market changes - complacency is your only enemy now.',
      qiuming: '有很好的机会，但须自强不息，刻苦努力，冷静分析。',
      qiumingEn: 'Great opportunities for recognition await. Keep working hard, stay analytical, and your talents will be noticed.',
      hunlian: '双方感情深厚，宜积极主动，但不可过于急躁，须知循序渐进。',
      hunlianEn: 'Love connections are strong. Take initiative, but don\'t rush. True relationships build step by step.',
      juece: '刚毅果断，精力充沛，必能成功。但须谦虚谨慎，不可锋芒毕露，更不可妄自尊大。',
      jueceEn: 'Your decisiveness and energy will bring success. But temper strength with humility. Hide your edge; avoid arrogance.'
    },
