      jingshangEn: 'Finances gradually prospering. Steady business. Don\'t rush. Gradual development.',
      qiuming: '学业渐进，稳步提高。循序渐进，终有成就。',
      qiumingEn: 'Studies gradually advancing. Steady improvement. Step by step. Eventually achieve.',
      hunlian: '感情渐入佳境，婚姻吉利。循序渐进，幸福美满。',
      hunlianEn: 'Love gradually improving. Marriage fortunate. Step by step. Happiness.',
