    xiang: '山上有火，旅；君子以明慎用刑，而不留狱。',
    xiangEn: 'Fire on the mountain - The Wanderer. The wise person is clear and careful in using punishments, not prolonging cases.',
    tuan: '旅，小亨，柔得中乎外，而顺乎刚，止而丽乎明，是以小亨，旅贞吉也。',
    tuanEn: 'Wanderer - small success. Yielding gains center outside, following the firm. Stopping yet attached to brightness - thus small success. Wanderer\'s steadfastness brings fortune.',
