      shiyun: '旅途漂泊，宜谨慎处世。',
      shiyunEn: 'Wandering journey. Be cautious in conduct.',
      caiyun: '经营流动，小有收益。',
      caiyunEn: 'Business mobile. Small gains.',
      jiazhai: '家有迁移；婚姻漂泊。',
      jiazhaiEn: 'Family moving. Marriage unstable.',
      shenti: '客居他乡，宜调养。',
