    xiang: '山上有雷，小过；君子以行过乎恭，丧过乎哀，用过乎俭。',
    xiangEn: 'Thunder on mountain - Small Exceeding. The wise person exceeds in respect, exceeds in mourning grief, exceeds in frugality.',
