    duanyiEn: 'Thunder on mountain - small exceeding. This represents slight excess, small matters. Small matters possible, great matters not. Be humble and low-key.',
    shaoYong: '山上有雷，小有过越；行过乎恭，用过乎俭。\n得此卦者，小事可做，大事不可。宜谦逊低调，不可张扬。',
    shaoYongEn: 'Thunder on mountain. Small exceeding. Exceed in respect, exceed in frugality.\nIf you receive this hexagram, small matters possible, great matters not. Be humble. Don\'t be ostentatious.',
